precis:
Amendments to the ACCOUNTING FOR IMPORTED GOODS AND PAYMENT OF DUTIES
REGULATIONS which establish a "billing period" and allow importers to
make a payment at any time between the time of accounting and the last
business day of the month during which the billing period ends.
